Class Summary
AbstractWatijGetTag Gets an HTML element stores it in the context.

WatijAssertTitleTag Asserts that the title is what is expected.

WatijContainsTextTag Looks for the given text on the page.

WatijHiddenTag Gets a hidden field and stores it in the context for use in another tag or the script.

WatijImageTag Gets an image on the page and stores in the context.

WatijSendKeysTag Sends keystrokes to the screen.

WatijSetHiddenTag Sets the value of a hidden field.

WatijSetSelectListTag Selects a given option of a select list.
WatijSetTextFieldTag Sets the value of a text, password, or textarea field.
WatijTextFieldTag Gets a text, password, or textarea field and stores it in the context for use in another tag or the script.
WatijTitleTag Gets the title of the page and stores it in the context.
